ions_Group2010\">Theatre Communications Group 2010</a>, p.&#160;511.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-FOOTNOTEWhitehouse20037-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEWhitehouse20037_7-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"#CITEREFWhitehouse2003\">Whitehouse 2003</a>, p.&#160;7.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-FOOTNOTEGroening2005-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEGroening2005_8-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"#CITEREFGroening2005\">Groening 2005</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-FOOTNOTECurtis2010-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-FOOTNOTECurtis2010_9-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"#CITEREFCurtis2010\">Curtis 2010</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-FOOTNOTECity_of_Belfast2011-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-FOOTNOTECity_of_Belfast2011_10-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"#CITEREFCity_of_Belfast2011\">City of Belfast 2011</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-FOOTNOTEhttp&#58;//bangordailynews.com/2017/01/05/business/new-owner-plans-co-housing-performance-space-for-old-belfast-high-school/-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEhttp://bangordailynews.com/2017/01/05/business/new-owner-plans-co-housing-performance-space-for-old-belfast-high-school/_11-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"#CITEREFhttp://bangordailynews.com/2017/01/05/business/new-owner-plans-co-housing-performance-space-for-old-belfast-high-school/\">http://bangordailynews.com/2017/01/05/business/new-owner-plans-co-housing-performance-space-for-old-belfast-high-school/</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-12\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://jlspal